node.text: Agnolotti, we like to party, we don’t cause trouble we don’t bother nobody 🎶🍝Cacio e Pepe Agnolotti from @alicerestaurantnyc - this pasta is sooo soft and melt in your mouth delicious! #pasta #NYCFoodComa

node.text: Highlights from the @lecreuset Hot Dish pop-up dinner at the new @dhamakanyc to celebrate the launch of their newest color - Cayenne! The last night of the Hot Dish pop-up dinner is tonight (8/11) and you don’t want to miss it - such a fun experience trying all of these new and exciting dishes! #CasuallyColorful #ad #NYCFoodComa

node.text:
Had a blast at the #SeaportArtois event last week! The perfect spot to celebrate summer with great pizza, beer, music, views and vibes! Top chefs from some of the best NYC restaurants are serving up their best slices alongside @stellaartoisusa. Check out the link in my bio for a chance to win a table at one of the upcoming events! [ad] #NYCFoodComa 

#eeeeeats #eater #nyc #nyceats #nycfood #foodie #foodporn #forkyeah #insiderfood #infatuation #tastethisnext #buzzfeast #eatfamous #dailyfoodfeed #newforkcity #tastingtable #nyceeeeeats #food #beautifulcuisines #feedfeed #eaterny #timeoutnewyork

node.text: Always sonny ☀️ Finally made it to @sonnyboy_nyc - highlights include the rigatoni with Burrata, the burger, fig & Burrata toast and the chicken parm. The burger was amazing and definitely a must! #burger #pasta #NYCFoodComa

node.text: Turning Taco Tuesday up a notch with the new @tacowaybeach x @caracasarepabar collab via the @doordash test kitchen! After struggling during the pandemic, these two restaurants teamed up with @doordash to bring a combined delivery & takeout service to Manhattan - you can order the former East Village  @caracasarepabar arepas and Rockaway Beach's @tacowaybeach tacos all at once for your next Taco Tuesday party or picnic! #ad #NYCFoodComa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NYCFoodComa • Jessica in Applebee's Grill + Bar with @applebees. May be an image of food.

node.text:
@applebees has a new Quesadilla Chicken Salad on their menu! It's served with grilled chicken on a bed of fresh greens tossed with
house-made cilantro ranch dressing and black bean corn salsa and topped with tortilla strips, house-made pico de gallo and served with a cheese quesadilla - YUM! It's also available for both to go and delivery! #ad #applebees #NYCFoodComa

node.text: FRYDAY 🍟🍟🍟 Lobster Cheese Fries in a four cheese sauce 😍 @redhooklobster #fries #lobster #NYCFoodComa

node.text: Spice spice baby 🍝 Spicy penne alla vodka from @serafinanewyork - one of my all time faves! Don’t forget to order the Tartufo Nero pizza! #pasta #vodkasauce #NYCFoodComa

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NYCFoodComa • Jessica in Applebee's Grill + Bar with @applebees. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text: @applebees has new summer salads on their menu to keep you feeling fresh this summer! This is the Buffalo Chicken Wedge Salad - a classic wedge salad taken up a notch with tomatoes, red onions, celery and topped with crispy tender boneless chicken tossed in Classic Buffalo sauce – finished off with Bleu cheese dressing. It's also served with a golden-brown signature breadstick brushed with buttery garlic and parsley. Available for both to go and delivery! #applebees #ad #NYCFoodComa
